title: Noisy Toyz - The Best Of
description:
Noisy Toyz are a female fronted, Symphonic rock band from Hampshire/London. 
The single "Trail of Tears" is from the New album "Forever one" album. the new album features Symphonic Orchestral hook lines to add to the theatrical edge,along with the melting pot of synth atmospheres, 7-string wall of guitar sound and drum grooves. 
They will take you on a musical journey with a variety of songs, some straight rocking tracks, some songs with an eastern feel, and some relaxing tracks with piano and violins.

Quality is 320kbps
